---
title: Tofu Chow Mein-Style Noodles with Stir-Fried Veggies and Peanuts
description: Savoury with a touch of sweetness, this dish combines tender-crisp veggies with irresistibly flavourful noodles! A final sprinkle of crunchy peanuts gives this dinner 10s across the board!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/nouilles-style-chow-mein-au-tofu-38e994f2.jpg
